media:group.media:title: Aerith in White Flower Bikini ★ Resident Evil 2 Remake x Final Fantasy 7 Remake Mods
media:group.media:description:
This video features Aerith Gainsborough from Final Fantasy 7 Remake replacing Claire Redfield in Resident Evil 2 Remake wearing white flower bikini using mods. Featuring several iconic Claire Redfield scenes. Hope you enjoy!

► Timestamps:

- 00:00 - Cloud & Aerith meet at gas station
- 01:29 - Cloud & Aerith get rammed by a truck
- 03:24 - Aerith saved by Biggs from a zombie
- 06:04 - Aerith finds Marlene in the boiler room
- 08:44 - Aerith & Marlene threatened by Don Corneo
